                        vaſt <expan>angenome<ex>n</ex></expan> hab </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_495_r1l15">v̈mb <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> willen / Des vvir
                                <expan>derſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan>
</ab>
<ab facs="#facs_495_r1l16">
<expan>fleiſſiklich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> dancken . vnd tun euch ʒu vviſſen .
